intent.user_query: Which product type has the highest number of open service tickets?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT p.ProductType, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS OpenTickets FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.Status <> 'Resolved' GROUP BY p.ProductType ORDER BY OpenTickets DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY OpenTickets DESC) <= 1;

arguments.sql: SELECT p.ProductType, COUNT(st.TicketID) AS OpenTickets FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets st JOIN fitness_db.Products p ON st.ProductID = p.ProductID WHERE st.Status <> 'Resolved' GROUP BY p.ProductType ORDER BY OpenTickets DESC QUALIFY ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY OpenTickets DESC) <= 1;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
